  },
  {
    "row": 121,
    "rowsha": "d7bqt4qrgYGHAssD2ilWsx+JXSsnWKrP7PUBOY0RruE=",
    "originContent": "- Releases run from pushes to `master` via `.github/workflows/ci.yml`.",
    "translatedContent": "- `semantic-release`는 Conventional Commit 메시지를 분석하고, 다음 버전을 계산하며, `CHANGELOG.md`를 업데이트하고, GitHub에 태그/릴리스를 생성하고, npm에 배포합니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 122,
    "rowsha": "wSGPZtpAgH4UTwCwP0IH49ruIXn4bK+Q1NAwANcoIBM=",
    "originContent": "- `semantic-release` analyzes Conventional Commit messages, computes the next version, updates `CHANGELOG.md`, tags/releases on GitHub, and publishes npm.",
